(1) Requirements
	pthread
	libcrypto
	libssl
	librt
	boost (uses boost/beast boost/asio)

(2) To get Boost
wget https://dl.bintray.com/boostorg/release/1.70.0/source/boost_1_70_0.tar.gz  # as of 8/2019
tar -xzf boost_1_70_0.tar.gz
cd boost_1_70_0
./bootstrap.sh  # build boost build engine
./b2            # complies boost
# installs to /usr/local/lib and /usr/local/include

(3) make

(4) ./bitstamp

(5) sample output
